# Global AI Governance Constraints

## 1. C# .NET Core Domain Rules
- All code under `src/PaymentsAPI/` is Tier 3. 
- Use `decimal` for all currency. No floats or doubles.

## 2. React Native & TypeScript Ecosystem Rules (Tier 2)
- All UI components under `src/mobile-app/` must use strict TypeScript types (`strict: true`). No usage of `any`.
- Functional components only. Use hooks for state management.
- Every API network request to the backend must explicitly inject an `X-Correlation-ID` header for end-to-end observability tracing.

## 3. Security & Observability
- Never print API tokens, user credit card data, or authentication states to `console.log`.
- All mobile diagnostic logging must route through the native transport layer to AWS CloudWatch.
